org.ma.ftc.lib.command

Class RobotMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ma.ftc.lib.command.RobotMap

  • public class RobotMap
extends java.lang.Object
    Singleton class that contains reference to general robot objects.

    This singleton class contains references to the hardware map, runtime, gamepad(s) and telemetry objects. It is initialized in the init(HardwareMap, Telemetry, ElapsedTime, MAGamepad) function.
